<div class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Design principles</h2>
  
  <div class="subsection">
    <h3 class="subsection-title">Typography guidelines</h3>
    
    <div class="principle-item">
      <h4 class="principle-title">✓ Use sentence case for headers</h4>
      <div class="principle-example good">
        <div class="example-text">Manage habits</div>
        <div class="example-text">Adding new habits</div>
        <div class="example-text">Set up next month</div>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-description">
        Headers use sentence case for better readability and a more conversational, journal-like feel.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="principle-item">
      <h4 class="principle-title">✗ Avoid ALL CAPS text</h4>
      <div class="principle-example bad">
        <div class="example-text">MANAGE HABITS</div>
        <div class="example-text">ADDING NEW HABITS</div>
        <div class="example-text">SET UP NEXT MONTH</div>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-description">
        All caps text feels aggressive and breaks the calm, handwritten journal aesthetic. It also has accessibility issues.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="principle-item">
      <h4 class="principle-title">Typography hierarchy</h4>
      <div class="principle-example neutral">
        <div class="example-text" style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;">Page title</div>
        <div class="example-text" style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 8px;">Section header</div>
        <div class="example-text" style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 4px;">Body text and descriptions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-description">
        Use size and opacity to create hierarchy, not case transformation.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="subsection">
    <h3 class="subsection-title">Interface principles</h3>
    
    <div class="principle-item">
      <h4 class="principle-title">Bullet journal aesthetic</h4>
      <div class="principle-description">
        The interface should feel like writing in a physical bullet journal - calm, organized, and handwritten.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="principle-item">
      <h4 class="principle-title">Minimal and functional</h4>
      <div class="principle-description">
        Every element serves a purpose. Avoid decorative elements that don't enhance usability.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>